"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:13:50.000Z","msg":"恆大當跌散紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48e6ce422718d1b8a302aff5bf3ce1adc33627b","tid":219411,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恆大當跌散紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n閉門/扣分"},{"pid":"07ca6d9f634bbfe111419eb7263a236190c1f18a","tid":219411,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>恆大當跌散紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n閉門/扣分</blockquote><br />\n初犯邊會，罰你幾萬至十萬<br />\n<br />\n舉多兩次啦，就停你賽勒"},{"pid":"3a02da5257f1bb10c92a02decf7c26cae5e5d677","tid":219411,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362dea84468eb68c105c7a4d6bf7399742656a78","tid":219411,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"強國水準？ 中、港足球大戰 中國球迷大罵「X你老母」<br />\n<br />\n2017-04-27 11:05<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕港超「東方龍獅」昨日在主場迎戰中超「廣州恒大」，最終以0：6落敗。但過程中「廣州恒大」球迷在場內高舉政治標語，甚至集體向香港球迷飆髒話，「東方龍獅」已就此事向官方反映。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，兩支球隊昨日於香港旺角球場對戰，雖然「恒大」以6分之差大勝對手，但有球迷在場內舉出「殲英犬、滅港毒」的標語，還集體向港人大聲怒罵「X你老母」、「漢奸」、「走狗」等不雅文字。<br />\n<br />\n這樣的行為獲得不少中國網友的讚賞，認為是在教「港燦」（對港人的貶稱）怎麼做人，還大讚飆髒話的舉動充滿「正義感」。有在場人士指出，中國球迷的舉動是因為場內有港人噓中國國歌、舉香港旗。<br />\n<br />\n由於比賽進行中出現政治、種族歧視標語，「東方龍獅」已在當下拍照存證，賽後向香港足總及亞洲足協委派的場監匯報，希望官方能公正調查此事並做出回應。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2049267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2049267&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=349b0aac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2049267&h=7ff6a92d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2049267</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1NkaGFsoYsw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1NkaGFsoYsw&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a19f1652\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1NkaGFsoYsw</a>"},{"pid":"d265687c045c61e713a1d08d674f2d0e25677a08","tid":219411,"uid":3280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:21:50.000Z","msg":"睇下大陸仔啲留言<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dongqiudi.com/article/321358\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dongqiudi.com%2Farticle%2F321358&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d741a1b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dongqiudi.com/article/321358</a><br />\n係咁話老豆教仔無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不如組隊過去挑機"},{"pid":"59fb93c93ff95c8b7b2faf4c3d54c968b4580ffd","tid":219411,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f164a345a8d9d2dea6edcb56de6ef07455ead2","tid":219411,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下大陸仔啲留言<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dongqiudi.com/article/321358\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dongqiudi.com%2Farticle%2F321358&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d741a1b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dongqiudi.com/article/321358</a><br />\n係咁話老豆教仔無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不如組隊過去挑機</blockquote><br />\non9同支那人有撚道理講架咩"},{"pid":"cf45c0d0933988043ce94ec9d7ed8e61d29b977d","tid":219411,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:27:46.0